{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 1902, "height": 2623, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "text", "block_content": "其二子：长治国，大学学历；幼国强，硕士研究生，均卓然成立。至公元二八年，渑池杜氏修祠续谱，乃捐资壹万元人民币以助修盛事，特予立石，以彰其德。\n", "block_bbox": [303, 238, 1735, 416], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "（——以上4碑为竖式，高1.32米，宽0.55米，平顶。）", "block_bbox": [407, 439, 1390, 485], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [137, 700, 210, 1362], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "修祠续谱功德碑", "block_bbox": [307, 502, 596, 547], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十八世杜智起，生于一九七四年十月三日，世居渑邑之北坻坞村。祖宗信，以农为本；父成金，积极于家族事业，两度修谱，其功甚多。智起迁居城关，兴办实业。为人乐善好施，重义轻财，于公元二O八年，渑池杜氏修祠续谱，乃捐资5888元人民币以助修祠盛事，特予铭石记功。\n", "block_bbox": [304, 570, 1734, 814], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "修祠续谱功德碑", "block_bbox": [308, 830, 597, 874], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "公元二八年，时当奥运之年，渑池杜氏乃举族而谋，修复宗祠、续编宗谱。十七世宗敏，少秉奇质，长而颖异，敦宗睦族，急公好义，致力于族谊和家乡事业，多所贡献。慨然出资伍千元以助修祠续谱盛举，值宗祠落成之时，特勒贞石以铭功德云。景敏，乃元吉之孙、宗堂之子，生于一九四七年五月，武汉水利水电学院毕业，本科学历，历任偃师县政府县长、洛阳市地矿局局长、洛阳市煤炭局局长等职。\n", "block_bbox": [304, 895, 1738, 1266], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "修祠续谱功德碑", "block_bbox": [308, 1282, 597, 1326], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜平泉，生于一九四九年十月十二日，渑邑之北坻坞村人，乃鼎和之孙、宗廉之子。其为人古道热肠，两度修谱，全力族事。办中学兴教育人，攻岐黄以医救人，特多贡献。其言传身示，家教有方，儿女皆硕士研究生，为我杜氏之秀。于公元二八年，渑池杜氏修祠续谱，出资伍千元人民币。值宗祠之成，特予铭石记功。\n", "block_bbox": [304, 1348, 1737, 1651], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "修祠续谱功德碑", "block_bbox": [310, 1671, 601, 1714], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜震，生于一九七七年五月十九日，家居县北之坻坞西村。其祖俊英，工于岐黄，精于医道，忠厚处世，关心族宜；其父文中，传承家学，业于县城。杜震古道热肠，敦于族谊，公元二八年，渑池杜氏修祠续谱，乃捐资伍千元人民币以助修祠盛事，特予立石，以彰其德。\n", "block_bbox": [308, 1735, 1734, 1979], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三七三", "block_bbox": [148, 1980, 196, 2092], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "修祠续谱功德碑", "block_bbox": [313, 1999, 601, 2042], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五世杜富礼，生于一九五八年二月五日，世居渑池仁村乡北坻坞村，现家渑池城关。其父玉琢，明于本草，尤精兽医。且为人厚道，不计钱财，故而医名闻于县北。富礼能承父志，和睦乡邻，热心公益，公元二八年，渑池杜氏修祠续谱，乃助资伍千元以襄盛举，特予立石，以彰其德。", "block_bbox": [307, 2063, 1734, 2308], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "(——以上5碑，均为横式长方形，平顶。)", "block_bbox": [412, 2332, 1162, 2374], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 15}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9392150640487671, "coordinate": [304.74542236328125, 1348.0709228515625, 1737.23095703125, 1651.2591552734375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9347171783447266, "coordinate": [308.459716796875, 1735.7470703125, 1734.485595703125, 1979.62109375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9261893630027771, "coordinate": [304.5328369140625, 895.7423095703125, 1738.0433349609375, 1266.0416259765625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9193740487098694, "coordinate": [307.83367919921875, 2063.84423828125, 1734.035888671875, 2308.408203125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9120909571647644, "coordinate": [303.56536865234375, 238.51220703125, 1735.84423828125, 416.8818359375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9076281785964966, "coordinate": [304.0828857421875, 570.19580078125, 1734.65869140625, 814.54248046875]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.8054037690162659, "coordinate": [310.37567138671875, 1671.808349609375, 601.3866577148438, 1714.022705078125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7953759431838989, "coordinate": [412.67120361328125, 2332.00341796875, 1162.85009765625, 2374.78564453125]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7908507585525513, "coordinate": [313.38421630859375, 1999.1214599609375, 601.5274047851562, 2042.3343505859375]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.769874632358551, "coordinate": [308.70855712890625, 1282.473388671875, 597.6853637695312, 1326.322998046875]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7600903511047363, "coordinate": [307.66827392578125, 502.3543395996094, 596.6253051757812, 547.0714111328125]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7472338080406189, "coordinate": [308.605712890625, 830.711181640625, 597.121337890625, 874.068115234375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6140145659446716, "coordinate": [407.0249938964844, 439.7042541503906, 1390.8226318359375, 485.7317810058594]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.4354016184806824, "coordinate": [148.54226684570312, 1980.53466796875, 196.95098876953125, 2092.6708984375]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.3782009184360504, "coordinate": [137.17654418945312, 700.8213500976562, 210.57965087890625, 1362.576171875]}]}, "overall_ocr_res": {"model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_textline_orientation": true}, "dt_polys": [[[312, 236], [1734, 246], [1734, 293], [311, 283]], [[315, 302], [1735, 310], [1735, 357], [314, 349]], [[311, 368], [455, 368], [455, 419], [311, 419]], [[413, 436], [1387, 441], [1387, 488], [413, 483]], [[313, 503], [592, 503], [592, 547], [313, 547]], [[393, 568], [1731, 573], [1731, 620], [393, 615]], [[313, 635], [1730, 641], [1730